data.description: Come home to this lovely 4 bedroom/2 bath ranch on a full basement in beautiful Mirror Lake golf, swim and tennis community.  Home has been well-maintained with lots of upgrades throughout including, new roof, new deck, new HVAC compressor, updated kitchen appliances, freshly painted kitchen cabinets, new kitchen flooring, recently installed Luxurious shower in Master Bath, new interior paint throughout and more!  Kitchen has view to family/great room.  Generous size Owner's suite with sitting area, tray ceilings and huge walk-in closet.  Master bath has double vanities and a gorgeous newly installed oversize tiled glass shower enclosure.  Spacious secondary bedrooms.  Private 2nd level 4th bedroom/bonus room is perfect for a teen suite or can be used for an office, workout room, study, etc.  Large unfinished basement has lots of potential.  Fenced backyard is perfect for kids, pets and family gatherings.  Mirror Lake offers lots of great ammenities including 2 or more community swimming pools, walking trails and much more!  Conveniently located near schools, shopping, restaurants and I-20.  Approximately 10 minutes to downtown Villa Rica with additional shopping, dining, amphitheater, concerts, movies and many other fun activities.  Make this home yours today and be a part of the wonderful life-style Mirror Lake has to offer!  Seller is offering $10k towards buyer's closing costs or interest rate buydown.  Some images are virtually staged.    If listing broker shows property to buyer's broker client, buyer's broker commission will be 2 percent.
